Developer Terms of Use
des:
Welcome to Dishwasher Pro, here to help you understand how to use and help maintain your dishwasher so you can get sparkling dishes every time.

With this skill you can:
• Get tips on how to load and clean your dishwasher
• Set monthly reminders to clean your dishwasher
• Hear tips for treating dishes that are cloudy, dirty, or not dry post-wash
• Receive tailored Finish® product recommendations to help maintain your dishwasher
• Easily add recommended products straight to your Amazon Shopping cart

Featured Finish products include:
1. Finish® Dual Action dishwasher cleaner
2. Finish® Quantum dishwasher detergent
3. Finish® Hard Water Booster
4. Finish® Jet-Dry rinse aid

Open the skill by saying: "Alexa, open Dishwasher Pro"

Or go straight to the section you need with these:

- To get tips to help maintain your dishwasher, say: "Alexa, ask Dishwasher Pro for dishwasher tips"
- To get tips for cleaning dishes, say: "Alexa, ask Dishwasher Pro for dishes tips"
- For Finish® product information, say: "Alexa, ask Dishwasher Pro for products"


*This skill uses Alexa Shopping to add items to your Amazon cart. Alexa can add products to your shopping cart by voice. You can see the product with delivery details and confirm the order by going to your Amazon account.
